<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Inactivity Alert</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }
    .header { background: #1a1a1f; color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .intro { color: #444; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .details { background: #fff; padding: 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #6366f1; }
    .suggestion { background: #f0f9ff; padding: 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9; color: #0c4a6e; }
    .footer { margin-top: 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 20px;">Inactivity Alert</h1>
    <p style="margin: 8px 0 0; opacity: 0.9;">Checkin – Emergency Contact Notification</p>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p class="intro">Hello,</p>
    <p class="intro">A user who listed you as an emergency contact has not logged in for {% if inactiveDays == 0 %}{{ inactiveDuration }}{% elseif inactiveDays == 1 %}the past day{% else %}the past {{ inactiveDays }} days{% endif %}.</p>
    <p class="intro">We wanted to let you know so you can check in with them if you have the chance.</p>
    <div class="details">
      <p><strong>User email:</strong> {{ userEmail }}</p>
      <p><strong>Last login:</strong> {{ lastLoginDate }}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="suggestion">
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>What you can do</strong></p>
      <p style="margin: 8px 0 0;">You can reach out to this person by mobile phone or email to confirm they are doing well. A quick call or message can help provide peace of mind.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      This is an automated message from Checkin. If you believe you received this in error, please ignore it.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
